rows.label: tlk70000014_02_msg0001
rows.name:
I've never seen the capital in
this kind of state before...

rows.label: tlk70000014_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Some guy has been following me
around a lot lately, too, which is
the last thing I need right now.

rows.label: tlk70000014_02_msg0003
rows.name:
He even keeps coming to the shop. I
think he's a traveling performer or
something... I wish he'd go away.

rows.label: tlk70000014_02_msg0004
rows.name:
He seems happy whether I'm rude to
him or even if I give him the silent
treatment. What's that all about?

rows.label: tlk70000014_02_msg0005
rows.name:
I guess he doesn't seem like
a bad person, at least.

rows.label: tlk70000014_02_msg0006
rows.name:
But I still just want him to leave
me alone. I'm not much of a people
person. I don't like being pestered.

rows.label: tlk70000014_02_msg0007
rows.name: How can I get him to understand that?!
